A Motion to File  M-1294 & Res 2116  was made; the Motion to File failed to garner the  26 votes necessary required  to file and was thereby defeated by the vote of 24 Affirmative-10 Negative-4 Abstentions.  
The vote was as follows:  
Affirmative--Boyland, Carrion, Clarke, DiBrienza, Eldridge, Foster, Freed, Koslowitz, Leffler, Linares, Lopez, Marshall, Michels, Miller, Perkins, Pinkett, Quinn, Reed, Rivera, Robinson, Rdriguez, Spigner, Warden, and  Watkins--24; 

Negative--Abel, Berman, Dear, Eisland, Oddo, O'Donovan, Povman, Provenzano, Ognibene and the Speaker (Council Member Vallone)--10; 

Not Voting (Abstain)--Malave-Dilan, Fisher, Henry, and McCaffrey--4.
